title: Micro Maxi Scooter
description:
Micro's highest-rated and most-awarded scooter for adventurous kids. 
Featuring an adjustable handlebar that grows with your child and a lightweight frame, making it easy for any rider to maneuver.

title: Micro Mini Scooter
description:
Micro's highest-rated and most-awarded scooter for eager youngsters. 
Featuring an adjustable handlebar that grows with your child and a lightweight frame, making it easy for even the littlest riders to maneuver.

title: Micro Maxi ECO Scooter
description:
Help the planet one scoot at a time on the Maxi ECO Scooter. 
Crafted from recycled fishing gear and maritime materials, this sustainable ride reduces manufacturing footprints while keeping harmful waste out of the oceans.
To learn more about our ECO Collection, visit our blog here.
